    tldr: 'Every small business has dead hours where fixed costs continue running but revenue barely trickles in. Your PoS hourly transaction data quantifies exactly when these dead periods occur, how much they cost you, and whether targeted interventions like flash promotions, staffing reductions, or alternative uses of the space can turn losses into at least break-even performance.',
